~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
    Defines input files and everything required to run a fast and simple pipeline test.

    Use as follows:
        next-flow run t~owï¿½Zï¿½ï¿½ï¿½|oï¿½ï¿½Lï¿½"ï¿½ï¿½|ï¿½ï¿½ï¿½ï¿-core/pacvar -profile test,<docker/singularity> --outdir <OUTDIR>

